0.Name: Victini
Desc: When it shares the infinite energy it creates, that being's entire body will be overflowing with power.

1.Name: Snivy
Desc: Being exposed to sunlight makes its movements swifter. It uses vines more adeptly than its hands.

2.Name: Servine
Desc: When it gets dirty, its leaves can't be used in photosynthesis, so it always keeps itself clean.

3.Name: Serperior
Desc: It only gives its all against strong opponents who are not fazed by the glare from Serperior's noble eyes.

4.Name: Tepig
Desc: It loves to eat roasted berries, but sometimes it gets too excited and burns them to a crisp.

5.Name: Pignite
Desc: The more it eats, the more fuel it has to make the fire in its stomach stronger. This fills it with even more power.

6.Name: Emboar
Desc: A flaring beard of fire is proof that it is fired up. It is adept at using many different moves.

7.Name: Oshawott
Desc: The scalchop on its stomach isn't just used for battle--it can be used to break open hard berries as well.

8.Name: Dewott
Desc: As a result of strict training, each Dewott learns different forms for using the scalchops.

9.Name: Samurott
Desc: In the time it takes a foe to blink, it can draw and sheathe the seamitars attached to its front legs.

10.Name: Patrat
Desc: Extremely cautious, one of them will always be on the lookout, but it won't notice a foe coming from behind.

11.Name: Watchog
Desc: Using luminescent matter, it makes its eyes and body glow and stuns attacking opponents.

12.Name: Purrloin
Desc: Their cute act is a ruse. They trick people and steal their valuables just to see the looks on their faces.

13.Name: Liepard
Desc: Their beautiful form comes from the muscles they have developed. They run silently in the night.

14.Name: Pidove
Desc: This very forgetful Pokmon will wait for a new order from its Trainer even though it already has one.

15.Name: Tranquill
Desc: No matter where in the world it goes, it knows where its nest is, so it never gets separated from its Trainer.

16.Name: Unfezant
Desc: Males swing the plumage on their heads to threaten others, but females are better at flying.

17.Name: Sawaddle
Desc: Since this Pokmon makes its own clothes out of leaves, it is a popular mascot for fashion designers.

18.Name: Swadloon
Desc: Preferring dark, damp places, it spends the entire day eating fallen leaves that lie around it.

19.Name: Leavanny
Desc: Upon finding a small Pokmon, it weaves clothing for it from leaves by using the sticky silk secreted from its mouth.

20.Name: Sunkern
Desc: It suddenly falls out of the sky in the morning. Knowing it's weak, it simply feeds until it evolves.

21.Name: Sunflora
Desc: Since it converts sunlight into energy, it is always looking in the direction of the sun.

297.Name: Kyurem
Desc: This legendary ice Pokemon waits for a hero to fill in the missing parts of its body with truth or ideals.
